text: "Disappear" is a 1990 song by Australian rock new wave band INXS and the second single from their seventh studio album X. It went to number 1 in Canada, number 5 in Portugal, number 8 in the United States (their last top ten single), number 9 in Ireland and the Netherlands and was a lesser hit in Australia, New Zealand and the United Kingdom.
